The app sends Express's default headers, which include `X-Powered-By: Express` (leaks technology stack) and lacks all protective headers (CSP, HSTS, X-Content-Type-Options, etc.).

**Recommendation:** Add `helmet`:

```js
const helmet = require('helmet');
app.use(helmet());
